This paper discusses the physical layer structure, monitoring mechanisms, beamforming operation, and carried information of the physical downlink control channel (PDCCH) in 5G NR. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Communications (cs.COMM), Augmented Reality (cs.AR), and Multiagent Systems (cs.MA) sub-categories.
